### Dropdown composition

Dropdown stacks four zones vertically: a label container, the field trigger, an overlay menu container (shown only when open), and a helper-text container. An error-text container and a left accent border are inserted between the field and helper text only in the Error validation state (see Dropdown — Error). The host container is 320 wide in the design source and carries no padding of its own; vertical spacing is owned by each zone.

