| layoutMode | vertical | Label, Field, Menu, Helper stack top-to-bottom |
| widthMode | fixed | 320 in the design source; expected fill/fluid in implementation |
| heightMode | hug | Height grows with visible zones |
| Label container | – | Holds the label text and the requirement marker |
