| Announcement | "Country, United Kingdom, dimmed" | |
| accessibilityTraits | .notEnabled | Marks the trigger as unavailable; VoiceOver speaks "dimmed". |
| Do NOT | keep the Field focusable when disabled | Remove it from the focus order and set .notEnabled. |

