| Property | Value | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Announcement | "Country, United Kingdom, drop-down list, disabled" | |
| disabled() | applied | Marks the control as not interactive; TalkBack appends "disabled". |
| Do NOT | keep the Field focusable when disabled | Set disabled() and remove it from the traversal order. |

